### JUST PERCHIN

Build your flock, find achievements and have FUN with Just Perchin!

## About

Just Perchin lets you choose your favorite birds and uses drag and drop functionality to do it! Certain combinations will get you some sweet achievements. Toggle between day and night mode! Check out everybirdie for unique feedback and bird blurbs. 11628 different combinations!

## Under the Hood

-Ruby ver 2.6.1
-Javascript
-Rails 6.0.3.2
-ActiveRecord ver 6.0 3.2
-SQLite3 ver 1.4
-Sinatra ver 2.0
-Sinatra ActiveRecord ver 2.0

## Install

To start building your flock, install locally by cloning the GitHub repositories. For the backend, run rails db:migrate, rails db:seed and rails s to start a local server. For the frontend, run lite-server.

## Code Highlights

```
function showInfo(birdId){
  const $target = document.querySelector(`h2[data-bird-id="${birdId}"]`)
  $target.parentElement.className = 'show'
  setTimeout(() => {$target.parentElement.className = 'invisible'}, 3000) 
}
```

```
  const allSame = score.every(value => value === score[0])
  if(allSame){
    achievementMaker('Achievement: Matchy Birdies')
